These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, tea
House: townhouse, futuristic, modern
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, western
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, mexican, polish
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, coral, turquise
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the indian##1
5. the mexican is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the townhouse house is between the person who likes red and the futuristic house##2
8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | tea     | milk      | fanta      |
| House          | futuristic   | townhouse   | modern       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | adventure | musical    |
| Nationality   | polish  | indian    | mexican    |
| Color           | coral    | turquise    | red |
| Transport     | subway  | train     | bus        |

