2. the havana-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the owner of the snake is the fan of folk##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growssunflower and the person eating nectarine##2
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | nectarine  | plum    | pumpkin   |
