4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
8. the entrepreneur is between the wooden house and the person driving the car##2
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
